1
00:00:10,450 --> 00:00:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was all pointless.</font>

2
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not pointless!</font>

3
00:00:15,210 --> 00:00:17,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you don't really want to quit!</font>

4
00:00:19,050 --> 00:00:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

5
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gave up your dreams to write manga 
and ended up an office worker.</font>

6
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

7
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The character writing's 
still a little weak.</font>

8
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

9
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How are you doing, Mi-chan?</i></font>

10
00:02:33,290 --> 00:02:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, it's just you, Dad.</i></font>

11
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:37,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, "Oh"?</font>

12
00:02:37,650 --> 00:02:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're making your dad sad!</font>

13
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, sorry.</font>

14
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just working, so...</font>

15
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's so late.</i></font>

16
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you overdoing it?</font>

17
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you eating decent meals?</font>

18
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:51,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure editing is no easy job.</font>

19
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially with scary superiors or 
manga writers who are hard to work with—</font>

20
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're choking!</i></font>

21
00:02:59,890 --> 00:03:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Calm down, and slow your words a bit.</i></font>

22
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Man, I've been coughing a lot lately.</i></font>

23
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I'm getting old.</i></font>

24
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, yes.</font>

25
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So? Why did you call me?</font>

26
00:03:15,370 --> 00:03:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, I don't really have 
a reason or anything...</i></font>

27
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, that's right.</i></font>

28
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Have you heard, Mi-chan?</i></font>

29
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Heard what?</i></font>

30
00:03:23,530 --> 00:03:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About Kizuki-kun.</font>

31
00:03:26,060 --> 00:03:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What about him?</i></font>

32
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from his mom that...</font>

33
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He quit his job.</i></font>

34
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

35
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font color="#7c7a78"><font color="#000000">From: Mitsuman Swimming School</font></font></font></font>

36
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#7c7a78"><font color="#000000">Subject: Inquiring about an interview.</font></font></font>

37
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#798585"><b>Koigahama City
<font size="22">Happe Park (Kugenuma Exercise Park)</font></b></font></font></font>

38
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks so much for scheduling 
this appointment, Nishino-san.</font>

39
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your work can be more convincing 
when you go out and do some research!</font>

40
00:03:58,950 --> 00:03:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

41
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for this opportunity.</font>

42
00:04:05,790 --> 00:04:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you around.</font>

43
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place hasn't changed...</font>

44
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you known 
about this place for a while?</font>

45
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the place my childhood 
friend used to swim.</font>

46
00:04:17,790 --> 00:04:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

47
00:04:20,150 --> 00:04:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I heard from his mom that...</i></font>

48
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right this way.</font>

49
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

50
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a big pool.</font>

51
00:04:39,030 --> 00:04:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The athlete you'll be 
interviewing is over there.</font>

52
00:04:44,610 --> 00:04:46,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

53
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?</i></font>

54
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho?</font>

55
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, something like that.</font>

56
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:31,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is great research material.</font>

57
00:06:31,110 --> 00:06:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

58
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hazawa-san?</font>

59
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry.</font>

60
00:06:41,470 --> 00:06:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you know...</font>

61
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I took a long hiatus from swimming, 
so my information could be a bit outdated.</font>

62
00:06:47,610 --> 00:06:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

63
00:06:52,300 --> 00:06:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because of my shoulder injury.</font>

64
00:06:54,100 --> 00:06:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of that, I had to completely 
step away from swimming at one point.</font>

65
00:06:57,970 --> 00:07:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In desperation, I ended up pushing away 
the people who supported me.</font>

66
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've made the decision 
to stop running away.</font>

67
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now I'm back.</font>

68
00:07:15,980 --> 00:07:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I even quit my job.</font>

69
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki...</i></font>

70
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He did that so he could 
go back to swimming.</i></font>

71
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a very serious commitment.</font>

72
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you have any doubts?</font>

73
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

74
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it's a reckless challenge.</font>

75
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

76
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want...</font>

77
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:40,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A specific person to see me again.</font>

78
00:07:48,030 --> 00:07:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, his shoulder isn't 
in tiptop shape just yet!</font>

79
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll heal. I guarantee it.</font>

80
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't slow down!</font>

81
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cool!</font>

82
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kizuki really shines when he's swimming.</i></font>

83
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:16,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're regaining your strength.</font>

84
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for everything today.</font>

85
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was able to get some great references.</font>

86
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't mention it.</font>

87
00:08:27,050 --> 00:08:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as it can help 
create something amazing.</font>

88
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to Hazawa-san, I think I have 
a solid idea for the main character.</font>

89
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

90
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is... Is something wrong?</font>

91
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Hazawa-san that childhood 
friend you mentioned earlier?</font>

92
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who swam.</font>

93
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:46,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

94
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was right!</font>

95
00:08:49,110 --> 00:08:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you a psychic, Kawaguchi-san?!</font>

96
00:08:51,530 --> 00:08:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you didn't know that 
he's been swimming again.</font>

97
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes...</font>

98
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He should have told me.</font>

99
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's your adolescence.</font>

100
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

101
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not...</font>

102
00:09:09,830 --> 00:09:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho!</font>

103
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki?</font>

104
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to see you.</font>

105
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

106
00:09:19,610 --> 00:09:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san.</font>

107
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, I... have all
 these ideas in my head!</font>

108
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going home to work on a draft!</font>

109
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, all right.</font>

110
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be heading out first!</font>

111
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Mizuho!</font>

112
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

113
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept running away 
for the past three years.</font>

114
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I selfishly hurt you.</font>

115
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really sorry!</font>

116
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It surprised me, you know?</font>

117
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I didn't think I'd see you here.</font>

118
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you still mad?</font>

119
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm mad. At myself.</font>

120
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't try to understand you at all.</font>

121
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe I told you "Don't give up" 
when you were suffering so much.</font>

122
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I could say was "Are you okay?" 
and kept cornering you.</font>

123
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong!</font>

124
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you encouraged me back then, 
I was able to come back again.</font>

125
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki...</font>

126
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho. I...</font>

127
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to aim to be 
a swimming athlete once more.</font>

128
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if I can ever
achieve my peak condition again.</font>

129
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I want to take back the things I lost.</font>

130
00:10:33,850 --> 00:10:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both swimming and you, Mizuho.</font>

131
00:10:36,430 --> 00:10:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki...</font>

132
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to make you fall 
for me again. I swear it.</font>

133
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm going to take a stand once more!</i></font>

134
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="18"><font color="#747272">I'm going to take
a stand once more!</font></font></font></font>

135
00:10:57,010 --> 00:10:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can see that the interview 
was useful, but...</i></font>

136
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?!</i></font>

137
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai. You're being so loud.</font>

138
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry.</font>

139
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been bugging me so much 
that I lost my composure.</font>

140
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how about you help me out 
a bit for a change of pace?</font>

141
00:11:16,370 --> 00:11:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

142
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, take a look.</font>

143
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see.</font>

144
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is this...?</font>

145
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm stuck on what to do next.</font>

146
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The two characters are about to confess.</font>

147
00:11:30,020 --> 00:11:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go out.</font>

148
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin...</font>

149
00:11:33,710 --> 00:11:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Shin, you...</font>

150
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see if I still like you, Mizuho.</font>

151
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to take back the things I lost.</font>

152
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both swimming and you, Mizuho.</font>

153
00:11:50,810 --> 00:11:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki...</font>

154
00:11:54,110 --> 00:11:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to make you fall 
for me again. I swear it.</font>

155
00:12:02,050 --> 00:12:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to think these things through, too.</i></font>

156
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something still bugging you?</font>

157
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Sakura.</font>

158
00:12:15,340 --> 00:12:16,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

159
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you do in this case?</font>

160
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if...</font>

161
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san!</font>

162
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a visitor 
waiting over at reception.</font>

163
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:26,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you.</font>

164
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't think 
I have any appointments.</font>

165
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

166
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They said their name is Kashiwagi-san.</font>

167
00:12:33,290 --> 00:12:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Kashiwagi?</font>

168
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Apparently, he's quite a looker.</font>

169
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's hot?!</font>

170
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your relationship with this guy?</font>

171
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Mizuho!</font>

172
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kai! What are you doing here?</font>

173
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to see you, Mizuho.</font>

174
00:12:55,810 --> 00:12:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

175
00:12:56,710 --> 00:13:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna quit your job and marry me?</font>

176
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a handsome high schooler.</font>

177
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marriage? How cute!</font>

178
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's it always Nishino-senpai!</font>

179
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way I'm doing that, idiot.</font>

180
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font color="#2fcfe6">Kai as a</font></font></font>

181
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="30"><font color="#1c90e0">kid</font></font></font></font>

182
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#2fcfe6">Shin's younger brother</font></font></font></font>

183
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just marry me already 
and come live with us!</font>

184
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:16,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so childish on the inside 
after all this time.</font>

185
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, are there manga artists here?</font>

186
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are not!</font>

187
00:13:21,770 --> 00:13:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

188
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about school, Kai?</font>

189
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About that...</font>

190
00:13:29,020 --> 00:13:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm visiting colleges for 
their open houses today.</font>

191
00:13:32,740 --> 00:13:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, here.</font>

192
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:39,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this to my workaholic brother.</font>

193
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? To Shin? Why?</font>

194
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's out sick with a cold right now.</font>

195
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:46,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So Mom made me bring all those things.</font>

196
00:13:46,450 --> 00:13:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm busy applying to schools
and it'd be bad for me to catch a cold.</font>

197
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why I'm leaving it to you!</font>

198
00:13:51,490 --> 00:13:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait, Kai!</font>

199
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't just dump this on me.</font>

200
00:13:55,410 --> 00:13:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

201
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would it bother you?</font>

202
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...</font>

203
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen 
between you and Shin?</font>

204
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nothing like that...</font>

205
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

206
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If this is something that 
makes you drag on like this,</font>

207
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should just choose me already!</font>

208
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh...</font>

209
00:14:18,710 --> 00:14:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If nothing's up, then 
you can pass it on to him.</font>

210
00:14:20,850 --> 00:14:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'm leaving it to you!</font>

211
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

212
00:14:54,120 --> 00:15:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#7691a6">Nishino</font></font></font>

213
00:14:57,590 --> 00:14:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho!</font>

214
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Shin!</font>

215
00:14:59,730 --> 00:15:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perfect timing.</font>

216
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's reschedule today's plans 
for another day.</font>

217
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

218
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki had an asthma attack.</font>

219
00:15:08,300 --> 00:15:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relay that to the others, okay?</font>

220
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to check on Kizuki!</font>

221
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah...</font>

222
00:15:21,350 --> 00:15:24,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mizuho... What am I to you?</i></font>

223
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:32,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

224
00:15:32,050 --> 00:15:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So loud...</font>

225
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho?</font>

226
00:15:44,950 --> 00:15:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

227
00:15:47,230 --> 00:15:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you fight with Kizuki?</font>

228
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin...</font>

229
00:15:51,430 --> 00:15:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congrats on making it 
into To-Ou University!</font>

230
00:15:59,190 --> 00:16:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy for you!</font>

231
00:16:01,930 --> 00:16:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. Thanks.</font>

232
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin-chan!</font>

233
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy for you!</font>

234
00:16:12,190 --> 00:16:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congrats! I believed in you!</font>

235
00:16:13,230 --> 00:16:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing! You studious nerd!</font>

236
00:16:14,930 --> 00:16:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, everyone.</font>

237
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've worked so hard for this.</font>

238
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#030e26">Congrats!</font></font>

239
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#002275">Everyone Got Accepted Into College!</font></b></font>

240
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="15"><font color="#091a31">(Airu got into technical school)</font></font></font>

241
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I fell asleep.</font>

242
00:16:49,970 --> 00:16:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's never going to be a day 
when Mizuho needs me.</i></font>

243
00:16:58,990 --> 00:17:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Thank you to all the 
athletes and individuals</i></font>

244
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}involved in today's swimming competition.</i></font>

245
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The competition 
has ended successfully and...</i></font>

246
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two look happy.</font>

247
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin-chan...</font>

248
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="20"><font color="#121f2d">
You'd better show up to the next lecture!
You'll lose your credits if you don't!

 Kuroda</font></font></font>

249
00:17:34,820 --> 00:17:36,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I don't do my best...</i></font>

250
00:17:38,870 --> 00:17:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mizuho would be happy.</i></font>

251
00:17:42,730 --> 00:17:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

252
00:17:43,930 --> 00:17:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the fireworks festival... 
Kizuki showed up.</font>

253
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

254
00:17:53,610 --> 00:17:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he came to see me.</font>

255
00:17:55,760 --> 00:18:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though Kizuki and I 
ended things a long time ago.</font>

256
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mizuho just won't let me give up.</i></font>

257
00:18:17,330 --> 00:18:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho?</font>

258
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry. Did I wake you up?</font>

259
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came.</font>

260
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

261
00:18:27,100 --> 00:18:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still have a fever, Shin. 
Are you okay?</font>

262
00:18:30,970 --> 00:18:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just took some medicine.</font>

263
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should kick in soon.</font>

264
00:18:35,730 --> 00:18:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, you should keep sleeping.</font>

265
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

266
00:18:39,810 --> 00:18:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

267
00:18:41,270 --> 00:18:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I put some stuff from Kai in your fridge.</font>

268
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll head out now...</font>

269
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't leave.</font>

270
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been jealous this whole time.</font>

271
00:18:52,250 --> 00:18:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whenever Kizuki was sick, 
he was able to keep you to himself.</font>

272
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin...</font>

273
00:19:09,390 --> 00:19:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Have you been keeping 
in touch with Kizuki?</font>

274
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">I'm going to make you fall 
for me again. I swear it.</font></font>

275
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

276
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't forgive him.</font>

277
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't forgive him for hurting you.</font>

278
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="22"><font color="#62574e">To: Shin
 Kai gave me some
side dishes from your mom.
They're in the fridge for you.
Get well soon.
From: Mizuho</font></font></font>

279
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin?!</font>

280
00:19:44,200 --> 00:19:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting you go anywhere, Mizuho.</font>

281
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho...</font>

282
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:53,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay by my side.</font>

283
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with you, Shin?!</font>

284
00:19:55,010 --> 00:19:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't like you at all!</font>

285
00:19:57,370 --> 00:19:58,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

286
00:20:13,970 --> 00:20:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin?</font>

287
00:20:16,760 --> 00:20:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He still has a fever.</font>

288
00:20:18,730 --> 00:20:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho...</font>

289
00:21:59,950 --> 00:22:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san?</font>

290
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:06,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kuroda-sensei...</font>

291
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Thank you for the other day.</font>

292
00:22:14,500 --> 00:22:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah. This is...</font>

293
00:22:16,650 --> 00:22:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought some things from 
Shin's mom. That's all!</font>

294
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, um...</font>

295
00:22:31,290 --> 00:22:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'll take my leave now!</font>

296
00:22:41,610 --> 00:22:43,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait.</font>

297
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask you something?</font>

298
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san...</font>

299
00:22:50,990 --> 00:22:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does Kashiwagi...</font>

300
00:22:54,620 --> 00:22:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does Kashiwagi mean to you exactly?</font>

301
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

302
00:23:04,330 --> 00:23:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin's... my childhood friend.</font>

303
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:11,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not fair.</font>

304
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

305
00:23:12,090 --> 00:23:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not fair!</font>

306
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you realize it?</font>

307
00:23:16,930 --> 00:23:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That Kashiwagi doesn't see you that way?</font>

308
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holding onto those feelings for so long...</font>

309
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really painful.</font>

310
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't keep seeing Kashiwagi like this.</font>

311
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I...</font>

312
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

313
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just being jealous.</font>

314
00:23:50,300 --> 00:23:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forget about this.</font>

315
00:24:09,930 --> 00:24:14,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><font color="#1b1e1a"># 22 Something I've Been Meaning to Say</font></font></font></font>

